// MICROFINANCE MODULE
// Full micro-lending platform: loan products, client registry, applications,
// disbursements, repayment schedules (flat & reducing balance), collections,
// arrears tracking, PAR (Portfolio At Risk) reporting.
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

